Usage: map_die_package [-help] [-output <string>] -package_model_file <string> {-die_mcp_header <string> | -net_pad_file_pair <string>}

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-die_mcp_header <string>             # <MCP header containing die abstract>
                                     # (string, optional)
-net_pad_file_pair <string>          # {{<net1> <pad file1>} {<net2> <pad
                                     # file2>}...} (string, optional)
-output <string>                     # <output directory of mapping results>
                                     # (string, optional)
-package_model_file <string>         # <package model file> (string, required)